    <h1>Wix Privacy Policy Generator</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Published July 18, 2026</p>

    <p>Wix does not ship a built-in privacy policy generator. The platform gives you a cookie consent banner and some GDPR toggles in the dashboard, but those are not substitutes for a full privacy policy document. To get one, you need a third-party tool. A <a href="https://buildprivacypolicy.com/">free privacy policy generator for your Wix site</a> asks targeted questions about your site's data practices, the third-party services you use (Google Analytics, Mailchimp, Stripe, Facebook Pixel, and so on), and which privacy laws apply to your visitors, then outputs a ready-to-publish policy you can paste into a Wix page. No signup, no payment.</p>

    <p>This guide covers the full picture for Wix site owners: why you need a privacy policy even if Wix does not force one on you, what the document must include to satisfy the GDPR and CCPA, how to add it to your Wix site step by step, and how to generate one in minutes rather than drafting from scratch.</p>

